name: Gunscape
blurb: Create, share and play your own FPS experiences. Mash-up your favourite classics into something amazing!

rewards.reward: BUILDER ============================= All launch themes (8 plus any custom user paid themes and stretch goals) + 50 level slots. Closed beta access June 2014. Exclusive Beta Kickstarter mini-theme that will include 1 weapon, 1 avatar and 2 props for you to use in your levels. "Founder" level status for map listings and forum account.

PLAYER ============================= All avatars forever.  You aren\u2019t interested in building levels, but you want access to all the avatars from the theme packs!  Closed beta access June 2014. "Founder" level status for your forum account.

CREATOR ============================= All themes forever (includes all future releases) + 200 level slots. Closed beta access June 2014. Exclusive Beta Kickstarter mini-theme that will include 1 weapon, 1 avatar and 2 props for you to use in your levels. "Founder" level status for map listings and forum account.

INCEPTION ============================= All themes forever (includes future releases) + 200 level slots. Exclusive First Alpha access March 2014! Exclusive Alpha Kickstarter mini-theme that will include the Beta Kickstarter mini-theme plus another 1 weapon, 1 avatar, 1 enemy and 2 props for you to use in your levels. "Founder" level status for map listings and forum account. Plus Digital Companion Art Book and OST included!
DOUBLE INCEPTION ============================== 2 x INCEPTION, that is, INCEPTION level rewards for 2 people.

EARLY MyFACE ============================= In-game avatar with your face (or some other graphic, kitty?) for your personal use only. No-one else can choose it, but everyone else can see it! We will create a digital version of your face which you can then apply to a set of player avatars.  Each new theme in the future will contain avatars for use with your face too. Also includes INCEPTION rewards.

Also includes INCEPTION rewards.  Closed Alpha access, but your face will take at most a month to get created.

EARLY MySKIN ============================= Custom avatar skin for your personal use only, no-one else can choose it, but everyone else can see it! Choose one of the player avatars and then choose a logo and colour scheme to be applied. This skin will work with your digitised face. Also includes MyFACE rewards.

MySKIN ============================= Custom avatar skin for your personal use only, no-one else can choose it, but everyone else can see it! Choose one of the player avatars and then choose a logo and colour scheme to be applied. This skin will work with your digitised face. Closed Alpha access, but your skin and face will take at most a month to get created. Also includes MyFACE rewards.

EARLY MySKIN TRIPLE ============================== 3 x MySKIN. Choose three of the player avatars and then choose a logo and colour scheme to be applied to each. This skin will work with your digitised face. Plus 2 extra INCEPTION reward packs.

MySKIN TRIPLE ============================== 3 x MySKIN. Choose three of the player avatars and then choose a logo and colour scheme to be applied to each. This skin will work with your digitised face. Plus 2 extra INCEPTION  reward packs. Closed Alpha access, but your skins and face will take at most a month to get created.

MyAVATAR ============================= One-of-a-kind custom modelled in-game avatar for your personal use only. You will have choice over what your avatar will look like, but will need to meet certain guidelines we have. If you theme it properly we can add it as a Theme boss too! Closed Alpha access, but your avatar will take at most a month to get created. Also includes MyFACE rewards plus 2 extra INCEPTION  reward packs.

EARLY MyIDEA ============================= Choose an old FPS theme and we\u2019ll add it to the game + your name (up to 8 names in case you group up with friends to fund this one) in the game credits! This theme will be in addition to the initial 8 themes. The theme will contain 15 blocks, 3 enemies, 1 boss, 2 player avatars and 2 music tracks by BoyVsBacteria. Also includes MyAVATAR rewards plus 7 extra INCEPTION  reward packs.
